20
00:01:08.390 --> 00:01:13.450
Once upon a time, there was a little pig.

21
00:01:13.550 --> 00:01:16.290
His name was George Pig. 

22
00:01:16.390 --> 00:01:20.349
And he was off to make his fortune. 

23
00:01:20.449 --> 00:01:24.420
Soon, he came to a forest.

24
00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:28.019
Do you like the story, George?

25
00:01:28.119 --> 00:01:32.329
Inside the forest was a little house.

26
00:01:32.429 --> 00:01:39.459
And inside the house was a bowl of porridge.

27
00:01:39.559 --> 00:01:42.650
George Pig was very hungry. 

28
00:01:42.750 --> 00:01:46.590
So he ate it all up. Yummy, yummy, yum. 

29
00:01:46.690 --> 00:01:51.536
But just as he finished, Baby Bear walked in, 

30
00:01:51.536 --> 00:01:56.256
and said, "Oy, did you eat my magic porridge?"

31
00:01:56.309 --> 00:01:58.599
George said, "Yes!"

32
00:01:58.699 --> 00:02:05.969
Baby Bear said, "that was magic porridge.
 It will make you go very big."

33
00:02:06.069 --> 00:02:10.030
And then George Pig began to grow. 

34
00:02:10.130 --> 00:02:13.686
He grew and he grew and he grew 

35
00:02:13.686 --> 00:02:18.556
 until he was taller 
than all of the trees in the forest.

36
00:02:18.589 --> 00:02:20.069
The end. 

37
00:02:20.169 --> 00:02:22.449
Are you sleepy, George?

38
00:02:22.549 --> 00:02:23.219
No. 

39
00:02:23.319 --> 00:02:25.620
Not even a little bit?

40
00:02:25.720 --> 00:02:26.620
No!

41
