 until he was the same little George Pig
 as he was before. 

63
00:03:51.539 --> 00:03:56.250
"How will we get back home now?" said Baby Bear. 

64
00:03:56.350 --> 00:04:00.099
"I can fly you home." said the dragon. 

65
00:04:00.199 --> 00:04:06.078
So George Pig and Baby Bear 
hopped on the dragon's back 

66
00:04:06.178 --> 00:04:13.528
